03204  * These registers specifiy the initial values used by the pseudo-random
03205  * sequence generators.
03206  *
03207  * Each of the 8 sequence generators uses 8 LFSRs to produce 8 x 16-bit
03208  * values at a time. In interation i, LFSR0 produces I(4i), LFSR1 produces
03209  * Q(4i), LFSR2 produces I(4i+1), ..., LFSR7 produces Q(4i+3).
03210  *
03211  * The initial value for LFSRx in PN generator y is specified by
03212  * RFIF_UL_PN_INIT(8y+x).
03213  *
03214  * The polynomial used is x(n+31) = x(n) + x(n+3).
03215  *
03216  * Each 16-bit I/Q sample is composed of 16 bits shifted from bit 0 of the
03217  * LFSR, starting at the most-significant bit of the sample.
